---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Services | High Tide Marketing"
  description="Full-service digital marketing powered by audience intelligence. Social media, paid ads, SEO, video, website design, and High Tide Radar — all built around your verified buyers."
  canonicalPath="/services"
>

<main>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="svc-pg-hero" aria-labelledby="services-pg-heading">
    <div class="svc-pg-hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="svc-pg-hero-inner">
      <span class="tag">Services</span>
      <h1 id="services-pg-heading">Every Service Is Powered by<br><em>the Same Intelligence.</em></h1>
      <p class="svc-pg-hero-sub">Before we run a single ad, post a single piece of content, or build a single page — we identify exactly who your buyers are. Everything we do runs off that data. That is what makes it work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE GRID -->
  <section class="svc-hub" aria-labelledby="svc-hub-heading">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 id="svc-hub-heading" class="svc-hub-heading reveal">What We Do</h2>

      <div class="svc-hub-grid">

        <a href="/services/social-media" class="svc-hub-card reveal d1">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 00-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 011-1h3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">01</div>
          <h3>Social Media</h3>
          <p>Organic content and paid campaigns that reach your verified buyers on Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok — not a demographic profile.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/video" class="svc-hub-card reveal d2">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="23 7 16 12 23 17 23 7"/><rect x="1" y="5" width="15" height="14" rx="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">02</div>
          <h3>Video &amp; Photography</h3>
          <p>Short-form social content, YouTube brand films, and client testimonials — produced end-to-end. We handle scripting, filming, editing, and deployment.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/websites" class="svc-hub-card reveal d3">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">03</div>
          <h3>Website Design</h3>
          <p>Custom-built websites that load fast, rank on Google, and convert the warm Radar traffic we send your way into real customers.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/paid-ads" class="svc-hub-card reveal d1">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 20V10M12 20V4M6 20v-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">04</div>
          <h3>Paid Advertising</h3>
          <p>Google, Meta, TikTok, and YouTube ad campaigns running off your verified buyer list — not a lookalike audience. Every dollar with a job.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/seo" class="svc-hub-card reveal d2">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">05</div>
          <h3>SEO</h3>
          <p>Technical SEO, local visibility, content built to rank, and link building — so buyers find you before they ever see a competitor's ad.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/radar" class="svc-hub-card svc-hub-card--radar reveal d3">
          <div class="svc-hub-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-hub-card-num">06</div>
          <h3>High Tide Radar</h3>
          <p>Our exclusive audience intelligence platform. Identifies your in-market buyers by name — before they fill out a form anywhere. The engine behind everything we do.</p>
          <span class="svc-hub-card-link">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="svc-hub-cta">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="svc-hub-cta-inner reveal">
        <span class="tag">Not Sure Where to Start?</span>
        <h2>Book a Free Strategy Call.<br><em>We Will Figure It Out Together.</em></h2>
        <p>We will look at your current marketing, identify what is working and what is bleeding budget, and show you exactly what we would do differently. No pitch deck. No pressure.</p>
        <a href="https://calendly.com/hightidemarketing/strategy-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-gold">Book Your Free Strategy Call →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

</Layout>
